<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Georama Drama"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="ジオラマドラマ"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Isekaijoucho"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="ヰ世界情緒"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="异世界情绪"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Georama Drama"/><amll:meta key="album" value="ジオラマドラマ"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="JPB602095249"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="2040000002"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="0026Qye00f5WIX"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="406403471"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="5XhMYCU954XYzYoJvGFkCB"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1687473810"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="174598250"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ASyunagi"/></metadata></head><body dur="2:45.620"><div begin="14.380" end="2:45.620"><p begin="14.380" end="20.640" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="14.380" end="15.020">愛</span><span begin="15.020" end="15.290">想</span><span begin="15.290" end="15.900">笑</span><span begin="15.900" end="16.020">い</span><span begin="16.020" end="17.720">が</span><span begin="18.270" end="18.480">上</span><span begin="18.480" end="18.680">手</span><span begin="18.680" end="18.860">く</span><span begin="18.860" end="19.070">な</span><span begin="19.070" end="19.240">っ</span><span begin="19.240" end="20.640">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">渐渐擅长挤出敷衍的笑</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">漸漸擅長擠出敷衍的笑</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Getting better at forced smiles</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">겉치레 웃음이 능숙해져서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je deviens meilleure pour les faux sourires</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Me he vuelto mejor fingiendo sonrisas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das erzwungene Lächeln fällt mir immer leichter</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Tornando-me boa em sorrir por conveniência</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я стала лучше притворно улыбаться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sono diventata brava con i sorrisi forzati</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aisowarai ga umaku natte</span></p><p begin="21.140" end="24.120" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="21.140" end="21.340">狡</span><span begin="21.340" end="21.540">猾</span><span begin="21.540" end="21.780">く</span><span begin="21.780" end="21.950">な</span><span begin="21.950" end="22.110">っ</span><span begin="22.110" end="22.970">て</span><span begin="22.970" end="23.180">い</span><span begin="23.180" end="24.120">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">也慢慢变得圆滑狡黠</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">也慢慢變得圓滑狡黠</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Becoming more cunning</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">점점 교활해져 가</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Et je deviens de plus en plus rusée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Y me voy volviendo más astuta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich werde immer listiger</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vou ficando cada vez mais astuta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И становлюсь всё хитрее</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E divento sempre più scaltra</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Zuruku natte iku</span></p><p begin="25.870" end="31.160" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="25.870" end="26.230">し</span><span begin="26.230" end="26.590">が</span><span begin="26.590" end="26.920">な</span><span begin="26.920" end="27.310">い</span><span begin="27.310" end="28.740">末</span><span begin="28.740" end="29.050">路</span><span begin="29.050" end="29.460">を</span> <span begin="29.770" end="29.990">踏</span><span begin="29.990" end="30.170">み</span><span begin="30.170" end="30.400">締</span><span begin="30.400" end="31.160">め</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">踩着微不足道的末路</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">踩著微不足道的末路</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Treading firmly upon a miserable end</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">보잘것없는 말로를 딛고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Foulant aux pieds une fin misérable</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pisando fuerte este final insignificante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auf das unbedeutende Ende tretend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Pisando firme em um fim insignificante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Ступая по своему жалкому финалу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Calpestando una fine miserevole</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shiganai matsuro o fumishime</span></p><p begin="31.580" end="35.600" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="31.580" end="32.300">確</span><span begin="32.300" end="32.700">か</span><span begin="32.700" end="33.060">め</span><span begin="33.060" end="33.420">て</span><span begin="33.420" end="33.780">る</span><span begin="34.070" end="34.500">よ</span><span begin="34.500" end="34.670">う</span><span begin="34.670" end="35.600">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">仿佛在反复确认什么</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">彷彿在反覆確認什麼</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">As if confirming it</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">확인하는 듯한</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Comme pour m&apos;en assurer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Como si estuviera asegurándome</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Als würde ich mich vergewissern</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Como se estivesse confirmando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Словно пытаясь в чём-то убедиться</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Come per averne la conferma</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tashikameteru you na</span></p><p begin="36.090" end="38.570" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="36.090" end="36.300">あ</span><span begin="36.300" end="36.540">な</span><span begin="36.810" end="37.020">た</span><span begin="37.020" end="37.230">が</span><span begin="37.520" end="37.690">く</span><span begin="37.690" end="37.900">れ</span><span begin="37.900" end="38.080">た</span><span begin="38.080" end="38.250">の</span><span begin="38.250" end="38.570">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你曾赠予我的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你曾贈予我的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">What you gave me was</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">당신이 준 것은</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce que tu m&apos;as offert</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Lo que tú me diste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Was du mir gabst war</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O que você me deu foi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">То что ты подарил мне</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ciò che tu mi hai donato</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Anata ga kureta no wa</span></p><p begin="38.790" end="41.510" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="38.790" end="38.990">あ</span><span begin="38.990" end="39.160">の</span><span begin="39.160" end="39.830">小</span><span begin="39.830" end="40.430">さ</span><span begin="40.430" end="40.570">な</span><span begin="40.570" end="40.960">箱</span><span begin="40.960" end="41.510">庭</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">是那座小小的袖珍庭院</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">是那座小小的袖珍庭院</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">That small miniature garden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그 작은 모형 정원</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">C&apos;est ce petit jardin miniature</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Fue aquel pequeño jardín en miniatura</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Jenes kleine Miniaturgärtchen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Aquele pequeno jardim em miniatura</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Тот маленький сад в коробке</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">È quel piccolo giardino in miniatura</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ano chiisana hakoniwa</span></p><p begin="41.510" end="46.230" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="41.510" end="41.680">触</span><span begin="41.680" end="41.840">れ</span><span begin="41.840" end="42.040">た</span><span begin="42.040" end="42.710">ら</span> <span begin="43.100" end="43.850">崩</span><span begin="43.850" end="44.190">れ</span><span begin="44.190" end="44.550">落</span><span begin="44.550" end="44.870">ち</span><span begin="44.870" end="45.990">そ</span><span begin="45.990" end="46.230">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">稍一碰触 便似要崩塌散落</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">稍一碰觸 便似要崩塌散落</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Seemingly about to crumble if touched</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">닿으면 무너져 내릴 것 같아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Qui semble prêt à s&apos;effondrer au moindre contact</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Si lo toco parece que se derrumbará</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wenn man es berührt scheint es zu zerfallen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Se eu tocar parece que vai desmoronar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Кажется он рассыплется если коснусь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sembra sul punto di crollare se lo sfioro</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Furetara kuzureochisou</span></p><p begin="47.780" end="50.000" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="47.780" end="48.110">演</span><span begin="48.110" end="48.320">じ</span><span begin="48.320" end="48.520">て</span> <span begin="48.700" end="49.040">僕</span><span begin="49.040" end="49.210">は</span><span begin="49.210" end="49.520">演</span><span begin="49.520" end="49.760">じ</span><span begin="49.760" end="50.000">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我扮演着 不停扮演着</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我扮演著 不停扮演著</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Acting, I am acting</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">연기하며 나는 연기하며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Jouant un rôle, je joue mon rôle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Actuando yo actuando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich spiele ich spiele meine Rolle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Interpretando eu vou interpretando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Играя я продолжаю играть</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Recito io recito</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Enjite boku wa enjite</span></p><p begin="50.110" end="52.650" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="50.110" end="50.470">深</span><span begin="50.470" end="50.640">く</span><span begin="50.640" end="51.010">臙</span><span begin="51.010" end="51.190">脂</span><span begin="51.190" end="51.560">の</span><span begin="51.560" end="52.650">糸</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">殷红如胭脂的丝线</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">殷紅如胭脂的絲線</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Deep carmine threads</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">짙은 연지색 실</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un fil d&apos;un carmin profond</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un hilo de un profundo carmesí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein tiefer karmesinroter Faden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O fio de um carmim profundo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Глубокие карминовые нити</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Un profondo filo color cremisi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Fukaku enji no ito</span></p><p begin="53.090" end="56.370" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="53.090" end="54.830">唇</span> <span begin="54.920" end="55.320">絡</span><span begin="55.320" end="55.510">ま</span><span begin="55.510" end="55.740">る</span><span begin="55.830" end="56.200">言</span><span begin="56.200" end="56.370">葉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">唇齿间 是纠缠不清的言语</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">唇齒間 是糾纏不清的言語</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Words tangled at my lips</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">입술에 얽히는 말들</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Sur mes lèvres, des mots s&apos;entremêlent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Palabras que se enredan en mis labios</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Worte die sich um meine Lippen schlingen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Lábios palavras emaranhadas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Слова запутавшиеся на губах</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sulle labbra parole intrecciate</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kuchibiru karamaru kotoba</span></p><p begin="56.380" end="59.270" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="56.380" end="56.770">僕</span><span begin="56.770" end="56.930">だ</span><span begin="56.930" end="57.190">け</span><span begin="57.300" end="57.490">の</span><span begin="57.490" end="57.830">色</span> <span begin="57.830" end="58.070">画</span><span begin="58.070" end="58.240">を</span> <span begin="58.240" end="58.710">描</span><span begin="58.710" end="58.930">く</span><span begin="58.930" end="59.080">の</span><span begin="59.080" end="59.270">さ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我要画出 只属于我的色彩与图景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我要畫出 只屬於我的色彩與圖景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Drawing colors and pictures that are mine alone</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나만의 색으로 그림을 그리는 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je dessine un tableau aux couleurs qui n&apos;appartiennent qu&apos;à moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pintaré un cuadro con mis propios colores</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein Bild in nur meinen Farben malen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vou pintar as cores e imagens só minhas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я нарисую картину в своих собственных цветах</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dipingo un quadro con i miei soli colori</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Boku dake no iro e o egaku no sa</span></p><p begin="59.270" end="1:04.490" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="59.270" end="59.640">断</span><span begin="59.640" end="59.810">じ</span><span begin="59.810" end="1:00.010">て</span><span begin="1:00.170" end="1:00.510">甘</span><span begin="1:00.510" end="1:00.700">く</span><span begin="1:00.700" end="1:01.010">賛</span><span begin="1:01.010" end="1:01.250">辞</span><span begin="1:01.250" end="1:01.420">を</span><span begin="1:01.610" end="1:01.980">贈</span><span begin="1:01.980" end="1:02.170">る</span><span begin="1:02.170" end="1:02.340">共</span><span begin="1:02.340" end="1:02.520">演</span><span begin="1:02.520" end="1:02.700">者</span><span begin="1:02.700" end="1:02.980">は</span><span begin="1:03.230" end="1:03.530">亡</span><span begin="1:03.530" end="1:04.490">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">绝不会有同伴 献上廉价的赞美</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">絕不會有同伴 獻上廉價的讚美</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Without any co-stars to offer sweet praise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">결단코 달콤한 찬사를 보낼 공연자는 없고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Il n&apos;y a absolument aucun partenaire pour m&apos;offrir de douces louanges</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Sin coprotagonistas que den elogios dulces con determinación</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es gibt keine Mitspieler die mir süßes Lob schenken</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Certamente não há coadjuvantes que ofereçam doces elogios</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Нет партнёров по сцене что одарят решительной и сладкой похвалой</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Non ci sono attori che offrano dolci lodi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Danjite amaku sanji o okuru enja wa naku</span></p><p begin="1:04.600" end="1:07.200" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:04.600" end="1:05.020">こ</span><span begin="1:05.020" end="1:05.300">の</span><span begin="1:05.560" end="1:05.830">役</span><span begin="1:05.830" end="1:06.110">名</span><span begin="1:06.110" end="1:06.270">は</span><span begin="1:06.270" end="1:06.640">借</span><span begin="1:06.640" end="1:06.830">り</span><span begin="1:06.830" end="1:07.200">物</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">就连这角色的名字 也是借来的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">就連這角色的名字 也是借來的</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">This role name is a borrowed thing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 배역의 이름은 빌려온 것</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce nom de scène n&apos;est qu&apos;un emprunt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El nombre de este papel es prestado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dieser Name meiner Rolle ist nur geborgt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Este nome do papel é emprestado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Имя этой роли взято взаймы</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il nome di questo ruolo è preso in prestito</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono namae wa karimono</span></p><p begin="1:07.370" end="1:10.340" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:07.370" end="1:07.540">い</span><span begin="1:07.540" end="1:07.710">つ</span><span begin="1:07.710" end="1:07.890">か</span><span begin="1:07.890" end="1:08.260">最</span><span begin="1:08.260" end="1:08.450">期</span><span begin="1:08.450" end="1:08.700">の</span><span begin="1:08.810" end="1:09.210">刻</span><span begin="1:09.210" end="1:09.350">を</span><span begin="1:09.350" end="1:09.710">待</span><span begin="1:09.710" end="1:09.880">っ</span><span begin="1:09.880" end="1:10.340">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">静静等待着 终末时刻的降临</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">靜靜等待著 終末時刻的降臨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Waiting for the final moment someday</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">언젠가 최후의 순간을 기다리며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Attendant un jour l&apos;instant ultime</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esperando algún día el momento final</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Irgendwann auf den letzten Augenblick wartend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Esperando algum dia pelo momento final</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Когда-нибудь дождавшись последнего часа</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In attesa dell&apos;ultimo istante un giorno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itsuka saigo no toki o matte</span></p><p begin="1:10.780" end="1:20.780" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:10.780" end="1:12.150">正</span><span begin="1:12.150" end="1:12.690">し</span><span begin="1:12.900" end="1:13.380">い</span><span begin="1:13.570" end="1:14.140">台</span><span begin="1:14.140" end="1:14.720">詞</span><span begin="1:14.720" end="1:15.150">で</span> <span begin="1:16.510" end="1:17.870">正</span><span begin="1:17.870" end="1:18.270">し</span><span begin="1:18.660" end="1:19.050">く</span><span begin="1:19.050" end="1:19.670">愛</span><span begin="1:19.670" end="1:20.110">し</span><span begin="1:20.110" end="1:20.470">て</span><span begin="1:20.470" end="1:20.780">ね</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">用正确的台词 好好地爱我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">用正確的台詞 好好地愛我吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">With the right lines, love me correctly okay</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">올바른 대사로 올바르게 사랑해 줘</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Avec les bonnes répliques, aime-moi comme il se doit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ámame correctamente con el guion correcto</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Liebe mich bitte mit den richtigen Worten auf die richtige Weise</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Com as falas certas me ame corretamente viu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Люби же меня правильно говоря правильные слова</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Con le battute giuste amami correttamente</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tadashii serifu de tadashiku aishite ne</span></p><p begin="1:23.270" end="1:32.310" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:23.270" end="1:24.030">物</span><span begin="1:24.030" end="1:24.960">語</span><span begin="1:24.960" end="1:26.790">は</span> <span begin="1:28.990" end="1:29.830">進</span><span begin="1:29.830" end="1:30.000">む</span><span begin="1:30.000" end="1:30.470">ば</span><span begin="1:30.470" end="1:30.910">か</span><span begin="1:30.910" end="1:31.270">り</span><span begin="1:31.270" end="1:32.310">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">故事只会一味地向前推进</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">故事只會一味地向前推進</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The story only keeps moving forward</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이야기는 나아갈 뿐이라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">L&apos;histoire ne fait que progresser</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La historia no hace más que avanzar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Geschichte schreitet nur immerfort voran</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A história apenas segue em frente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">История лишь продолжает идти вперёд</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La storia non fa altro che avanzare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Monogatari wa susumu bakari de</span></p><p begin="1:34.780" end="1:40.150" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:34.780" end="1:35.210">し</span><span begin="1:35.210" end="1:35.570">が</span><span begin="1:35.570" end="1:35.940">な</span><span begin="1:35.940" end="1:36.240">い</span><span begin="1:36.240" end="1:37.690">最</span><span begin="1:37.690" end="1:38.040">期</span><span begin="1:38.040" end="1:38.570">を</span><span begin="1:38.810" end="1:39.170">恐</span><span begin="1:39.170" end="1:39.350">れ</span><span begin="1:39.350" end="1:40.150">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">畏惧着微不足道的结局</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">畏懼著微不足道的結局</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Fearing a miserable end</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">보잘것없는 최후를 두려워하며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Craignant une fin misérable</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Temiendo un final insignificante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das unbedeutende Ende fürchtend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Temendo o fim insignificante</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Боясь своего жалкого конца</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Temendo una fine miserevole</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shiganai saigo o osorete</span></p><p begin="1:40.510" end="1:44.700" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:40.510" end="1:40.790">張</span><span begin="1:40.790" end="1:41.300">り</span><span begin="1:41.300" end="1:41.660">付</span><span begin="1:41.660" end="1:42.020">く</span><span begin="1:42.020" end="1:42.410">ペ</span><span begin="1:42.410" end="1:43.030">ル</span><span begin="1:43.030" end="1:43.640">ソ</span><span begin="1:43.640" end="1:44.700">ナ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">紧紧依附的假面 无法剥离</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">緊緊依附的假面 無法剝離</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">A persona sticking fast</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">달라붙어 떨어지지 않는 페르소나</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Cette persona qui reste collée à moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mi persona está adherida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Persona die fest an mir klebt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A persona que está grudada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Приросшая маска которую не снять</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La maschera rimasta incollata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Haritsuku perusona</span></p><p begin="1:45.030" end="1:47.530" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:45.030" end="1:45.270">こ</span><span begin="1:45.270" end="1:45.490">の</span><span begin="1:45.800" end="1:46.330">歌</span><span begin="1:46.330" end="1:46.500">が</span><span begin="1:46.500" end="1:46.870">示</span><span begin="1:46.870" end="1:47.060">す</span><span begin="1:47.060" end="1:47.240">も</span><span begin="1:47.240" end="1:47.530">の</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">这首歌所昭示的一切</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">這首歌所昭示的一切</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">What this song indicates</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 노래가 나타내는 것</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce que cette chanson indique</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Lo que esta canción muestra</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Was dieses Lied offenbart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O que esta canção indica</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">То на что указывает эта песня</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ciò che questa canzone indica</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono uta ga shimesu mono</span></p><p begin="1:47.760" end="1:50.360" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:47.760" end="1:48.140">僕</span><span begin="1:48.140" end="1:48.340">が</span><span begin="1:48.640" end="1:48.840">詰</span><span begin="1:48.840" end="1:49.200">め</span><span begin="1:49.200" end="1:49.370">た</span><span begin="1:49.370" end="1:49.760">思</span><span begin="1:49.760" end="1:50.110">惑</span><span begin="1:50.110" end="1:50.360">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">还有我藏在其中的心思</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">還有我藏在心中的心思</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The intentions I&apos;ve packed inside</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">내가 채워 넣은 속셈을</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Les intentions que j&apos;y ai enfermées</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Las intenciones que he guardado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Absichten die ich hineingelegt habe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">As intenções que eu guardei</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Те замыслы что я в неё вложила</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Le intenzioni che ho racchiuso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Boku ga tsumeta omowaku o</span></p><p begin="1:50.640" end="1:55.890" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:50.640" end="1:50.850">あ</span><span begin="1:50.850" end="1:51.020">な</span><span begin="1:51.020" end="1:51.370">た</span><span begin="1:51.370" end="1:51.690">が</span><span begin="1:51.690" end="1:52.110">知</span><span begin="1:52.110" end="1:52.470">る</span><span begin="1:52.470" end="1:53.190">由</span><span begin="1:53.190" end="1:53.520">も</span><span begin="1:53.520" end="1:53.910">な</span><span begin="1:53.910" end="1:54.760">い</span><span begin="1:54.960" end="1:55.140">で</span><span begin="1:55.140" end="1:55.230">し</span><span begin="1:55.230" end="1:55.700">ょ</span><span begin="1:55.700" end="1:55.890">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你大概 从来都不曾知晓吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">你大概 從來都不曾知曉吧</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">You probably have no way of knowing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">당신이 알 리 없겠지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Tu n&apos;as sûrement aucun moyen de les connaître n&apos;est-ce pas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Seguramente no tienes forma de saberlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Du wirst wohl keine Möglichkeit haben sie zu kennen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Você provavelmente não tem como saber não é?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Тебе наверняка никогда не узнать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Probabilmente non avrai modo di saperlo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Anata ga shiru yoshi mo nai deshou</span></p><p begin="1:56.560" end="1:59.060" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:56.560" end="1:57.120">曖</span><span begin="1:57.280" end="1:57.820">昧</span><span begin="1:58.010" end="1:58.180">な</span><span begin="1:58.180" end="1:58.450">身</span><span begin="1:58.450" end="1:58.730">体</span><span begin="1:58.730" end="1:59.060">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">模糊的身躯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">模糊的身軀</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">This ambiguous body</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">애매한 신체는</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce corps ambigu</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Mi cuerpo ambiguo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mein verschwommener Körper</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O corpo vago</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Моё призрачное тело</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il corpo ambiguo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aimai na karada wa</span></p><p begin="1:59.260" end="2:01.890" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:59.260" end="1:59.610">空</span><span begin="1:59.610" end="2:00.000">に</span><span begin="2:00.120" end="2:00.870">宙</span><span begin="2:00.870" end="2:01.040">に</span> <span begin="2:01.040" end="2:01.440">解</span><span begin="2:01.440" end="2:01.600">れ</span><span begin="2:01.600" end="2:01.890">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在半空之中 渐渐松散 瓦解</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在半空之中 漸漸鬆散 瓦解</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Unraveling into the sky and air</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">허공 속에서 풀려나</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">S&apos;effiloche dans les airs, dans le vide</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Se deshilacha en el aire en el espacio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Löst sich in der Leere des Himmels auf</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">No céu no ar desfazendo-se</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Распутывается и тает в пустоте</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Si scioglie nel vuoto e nel cielo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kuu ni chuu ni hogurete</span></p><p begin="2:02.150" end="2:06.860" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:02.150" end="2:02.500">今</span><span begin="2:02.500" end="2:03.210">に</span><span begin="2:03.540" end="2:04.340">崩</span><span begin="2:04.340" end="2:04.670">れ</span><span begin="2:04.670" end="2:05.020">落</span><span begin="2:05.020" end="2:05.390">ち</span><span begin="2:05.390" end="2:06.600">そ</span><span begin="2:06.600" end="2:06.860">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">此刻仿佛 下一秒就要崩塌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">此刻彷彿 下一秒就要崩塌</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Seemingly about to crumble at any moment</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">금방이라도 무너져 내릴 것 같아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Prêt à s&apos;effondrer d&apos;un instant à l&apos;autre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Siento que va a derrumbarse ahora mismo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Scheint jeden Moment in sich zusammenzufallen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Parece que vai desmoronar a qualquer momento</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Кажется оно вот-вот рассыплется</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sembra sul punto di crollare proprio ora</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ima ni kuzureochisou</span></p><p begin="2:09.580" end="2:11.870" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:09.580" end="2:10.010">演</span><span begin="2:10.010" end="2:10.240">じ</span><span begin="2:10.240" end="2:10.500">て</span> <span begin="2:10.600" end="2:10.960">僕</span><span begin="2:10.960" end="2:11.140">は</span><span begin="2:11.140" end="2:11.430">演</span><span begin="2:11.430" end="2:11.660">じ</span><span begin="2:11.660" end="2:11.870">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我扮演着 不停扮演着</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我扮演著 不停扮演著</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Acting, I am acting</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">연기하며 나는 연기하며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Jouant un rôle, je joue mon rôle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Actuando yo actuando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich spiele ich spiele meine Rolle</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Interpretando eu vou interpretando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Играя я продолжаю играть</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Recito io recito</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Enjite boku wa enjite</span></p><p begin="2:12.020" end="2:14.590" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:12.020" end="2:12.380">深</span><span begin="2:12.380" end="2:12.570">く</span><span begin="2:12.570" end="2:12.900">臙</span><span begin="2:12.900" end="2:13.120">脂</span><span begin="2:13.120" end="2:13.480">の</span><span begin="2:13.480" end="2:14.590">糸</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">殷红如胭脂的丝线</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">殷紅如胭脂的絲線</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Deep carmine threads</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">짙은 연지색 실</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Un fil d&apos;un carmin profond</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un hilo de un profundo carmesí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein tiefer karmesinroter Faden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O fio de um carmim profundo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Глубокие карминовые нити</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Un profondo filo color cremisi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Fukaku enji no ito</span></p><p begin="2:15.050" end="2:18.320" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:15.050" end="2:16.820">唇</span> <span begin="2:16.820" end="2:17.250">絡</span><span begin="2:17.250" end="2:17.430">ま</span><span begin="2:17.430" end="2:17.650">る</span><span begin="2:17.740" end="2:18.140">言</span><span begin="2:18.140" end="2:18.320">葉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">唇齿间 是纠缠不清的言语</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">唇齒間 是糾纏不清的言語</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Words tangled at my lips</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">입술에 얽히는 말들</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Sur mes lèvres, des mots s&apos;entremêlent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Palabras que se enredan en mis labios</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Worte die sich um meine Lippen schlingen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Lábios palavras emaranhadas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Слова запутавшиеся на губах</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sulle labbra parole intrecciate</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kuchibiru karamaru kotoba</span></p><p begin="2:18.320" end="2:21.160" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:18.320" end="2:18.680">僕</span><span begin="2:18.680" end="2:18.840">だ</span><span begin="2:18.840" end="2:19.110">け</span><span begin="2:19.220" end="2:19.410">の</span><span begin="2:19.410" end="2:19.750">色</span> <span begin="2:19.750" end="2:19.970">画</span><span begin="2:19.970" end="2:20.150">を</span> <span begin="2:20.150" end="2:20.620">描</span><span begin="2:20.620" end="2:20.840">く</span><span begin="2:20.840" end="2:21.000">の</span><span begin="2:21.000" end="2:21.160">さ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我要画出 只属于我的色彩与图景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我要畫出 只屬於我的色彩與圖景</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Drawing colors and pictures that are mine alone</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나만의 색으로 그림을 그리는 거야</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je dessine un tableau aux couleurs qui n&apos;appartiennent qu&apos;à moi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Pintaré un cuadro con mis propios colores</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ein Bild in nur meinen Farben malen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Vou pintar as cores e imagens só minhas</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я нарисую картину в своих собственных цветах</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Dipingo un quadro con i miei soli colori</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Boku dake no iro e o egaku no sa</span></p><p begin="2:21.160" end="2:23.330" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:21.160" end="2:21.540">案</span><span begin="2:21.540" end="2:21.720">じ</span><span begin="2:21.720" end="2:21.940">て</span><span begin="2:22.080" end="2:22.480">覆</span><span begin="2:22.480" end="2:22.600">う</span><span begin="2:22.600" end="2:22.990">惨</span><span begin="2:22.990" end="2:23.180">事</span><span begin="2:23.180" end="2:23.330">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">将令人担忧的 覆满阴霾的惨事</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">將令人擔憂的 覆滿陰霾的慘事</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The catastrophe covered in anxiety</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">걱정하며 뒤덮는 참극을</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Couvrant le désastre inquiétant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La tragedia que cubro preocupada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die besorgniserregende Tragödie verdeckend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A tragédia que cubro por preocupação</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Все эти тревожные бедствия</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Coprendo il disastro che mi preoccupa</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Anjite oou sanji o</span></p><p begin="2:23.520" end="2:26.270" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:23.520" end="2:23.720">エ</span><span begin="2:23.720" end="2:23.900">ン</span><span begin="2:23.900" end="2:24.080">ド</span><span begin="2:24.080" end="2:24.320">ロ</span><span begin="2:24.320" end="2:24.560">ー</span><span begin="2:24.560" end="2:24.790">ル</span><span begin="2:24.790" end="2:25.010">に</span><span beg