n" xml:lang="pt">Este nome do papel é emprestado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Имя этой роли взято взаймы</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il nome di questo ruolo è preso in prestito</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono namae wa karimono</span></p><p begin="2:29.280" end="2:32.090" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:29.280" end="2:29.460">い</span><span begin="2:29.460" end="2:29.640">つ</span><span begin="2:29.640" end="2:29.820">か</span><span begin="2:29.820" end="2:30.160">最</span><span begin="2:30.160" end="2:30.360">期</span><span begin="2:30.360" end="2:30.700">の</span><span begin="2:30.700" end="2:31.090">刻</span><span begin="2:31.090" end="2:31.280">を</span><span begin="2:31.280" end="2:31.530">待</span><span begin="2:31.530" end="2:31.780">っ</span><span begin="2:31.780" end="2:32.090">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">静静等待着 终末时刻的降临</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">靜靜等待著 終末時刻的降臨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Waiting for the final moment someday</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">언젠가 최후의 순간을 기다리며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Attendant un jour l&apos;instant ultime</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Esperando algún día el momento final</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Irgendwann auf den letzten Augenblick wartend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Esperando algum dia pelo momento final</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Когда-нибудь дождавшись последнего часа</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In attesa dell&apos;ultimo istante un giorno</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Itsuka saigo no toki o matte</span></p><p begin="2:32.310" end="2:34.950" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:32.310" end="2:32.700">こ</span><span begin="2:32.700" end="2:32.900">の</span><span begin="2:33.230" end="2:33.500">人</span><span begin="2:33.500" end="2:33.770">生</span><span begin="2:33.770" end="2:33.940">を</span><span begin="2:33.940" end="2:34.500">還</span><span begin="2:34.500" end="2:34.670">し</span><span begin="2:34.670" end="2:34.950">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">把这短暂的人生 归还回去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">把這短暫的人生 歸還回去</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Returning this life</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">이 인생을 돌려주고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">En rendant cette vie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Devolviendo esta vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Dieses Leben zurückgebend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Devolvendo esta vida</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Верни мне эту жизнь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Restituendo questa vita</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kono subete o kaeshite</span></p><p begin="2:35.000" end="2:39.820" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:35.000" end="2:35.210">そ</span><span begin="2:35.210" end="2:35.380">の</span><span begin="2:35.380" end="2:35.720">時</span> <span begin="2:35.720" end="2:36.350">心</span><span begin="2:36.460" end="2:36.640">か</span><span begin="2:36.640" end="2:36.840">ら</span><span begin="2:36.840" end="2:37.370">笑</span><span begin="2:37.370" end="2:37.550">い</span><span begin="2:37.550" end="2:37.970">た</span><span begin="2:37.970" end="2:38.090">い</span><span begin="2:38.090" end="2:38.460">だ</span><span begin="2:38.460" end="2:39.820">け</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">只盼望那时 能从心底真正笑一次</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">只盼望那時 能從心底真正笑一次</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">At that time I just want to laugh from the heart</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그때 마음껏 웃고 싶을 뿐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je veux seulement pouvoir rire de tout mon cœur à ce moment-là</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">En ese momento solo quiero reír de corazón</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">In jenem Moment möchte ich einfach nur von Herzen lachen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Naquela hora só quero sorrir de coração</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В тот миг я просто хочу рассмеяться от всего сердца</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Voglio solo sorridere dal cuore in quel momento</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono toki kokoro kara waraitai dake</span></p><p begin="2:43.830" end="2:45.620" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:43.830" end="2:44.190">だ</span><span begin="2:44.190" end="2:45.620">け</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">仅此而已</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">僅此而已</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Just that</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그뿐</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Seulement</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Solo eso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Einfach nur</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Apenas isso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И только</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Solo questo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dake</span></p></div></body></tt>